title: Pool open year round!
posting_body: Exceptional Apartment Homes in Northwest Austin, Texas Station our pet-friendly apartment homes give you everything you want and need in your next home.
Our unparalleled apartment homes offer a range of floor plans including one, two and three- bedroom options.
From in-home washers and dryers to extra large soaking tubs, our apartment interiors combine all the most important features you want.
Around the community, you can find a year-round resort style pool and garages, making living even better beyond your front door.
Ideally located off I-45 in Northwest Austin, our community provides you access to dining, shopping, arts, entertainment and recreation.

Take the Station MetroRail to Lakeline Mall, visit Austin Aquarium or have a night out with dinner and a movie at the Alamo Drafthouse Cinema Lakeline—all easily accessible when you choose an apartment home at  Lakeline Station.
Schedule your tour today and see why living at Lakeline Station is the best of Northwest Austin.
